9... Qxd7 10. Nc3 O-O
{ 10...b5  can also come now, but not with tempo, because there is no bishop on a4. White can reply with  11.Bg5  , for example. }
11. O-O b5 12. Bg5
{ Black doesn't solve the problems and White keeps the massive pawn center. } *

