6... Nxd5 7. Qd1
{ Simple and rare, but still good. White clears the way for the development of the f1-bishop and removes the queen from the e-file. Black is unable to create complications, while we end the development with Bc4 and O-O. }
7... O-O 8. Bc4 Nc6 9. h3
