{ White moves the queen away with tempo and gains time for development. } 6...
c6 7. dxc6
{ Why not take another pawn? We're not so far behind in development that it would be a cause for concern... }
7... O-O 8. cxb7 Bxb7 9. Be2
{ White is winning. We are three pawns up. More importantly, however, Black has no chance of preventing us from castling and we have no problem getting our king to safety. }
