Bb5
{ The refutation of 6... Nc6?. However, White needs to know a few more precise moves. }
7... Bd7 8. Bg5
{ Only move, Black can't capture on g5 because of the discovered attack on the e-file. }
8... f6 9. Nc3
{ And the black position can no longer cope with the penetration of the knight on d5. }
9... dxe5 10. Nd5
{ White wins material, for example:  10...Qd6  11.dxe5  Nxe5  12.Bxd7+  Qxd7  13.Bxf6  . }
