{ White establishes the knight on e5 and is ready to chase away their opponent's with f2-f3 @@StartBracket@@Black no longer has the same option with ...f7-f6@@EndBracket@@.   If the white knight is later challenged with ... Nc6 later, the rook from e1 or the bishop from c1 are ready to follow up on e5. }
