{ White forces the transformation of the position, Black must go for it, otherwise White already has an extra pawn. }
12... Bxh2+ 13. Nxh2 Qxd5 14. Nf3
{ White is better, the outpost e5 is excellent. In addition, Black is weakened by ...f7-f5 on the long diagonal and the absence of the black-squared bishop will also make itself felt. }
