{ 9...Bxc3+  10.bxc3!  +-, White absolutely must capture with the pawn so that the pin on the d-file remains and Black cannot reply with ...Nxe5. }
10. Nxd7+ { Now White simply wins because on  10...Ke7  Qxg7+  is possible. } *

