{ The simplest move, White gets a big advantage and can play natural developing moves.   6.Bxf7+  would even be stronger, but I don't recommend it because it's also much more complicated to play. After  6...Kf8  O-O  White has to find many accurate moves, which is why this approach seems impractical to me. }
