7. Qg4 Qf6
{ This has been played almost exclusively so far. Black protects g7 without irreversibly weakening the structure with ...g7-g6 and sets up the threat ... d7-d5 winning a piece. }
8. Nc3
{ Provocative, but strong! What do you think White has planned after the discovered attack with  8...d5 ? }
