Nge7 14. Rad1 { Ties up the d-pawn and prepares e4-e5. } 14... O-O 15. e5 Ng6
16. exd6 Nxf4 17. Rxf4 cxd6 18. Rf2
{ White prevents ...Qb6+ before finally winning back the pawn and settling into an equal endgame. }
