8. Nxf7 Nxf7 9. Bxf7+ Kxf7 10. cxb4 Nf6
{ This is objectively the lesser evil, but here White has easy moves. The e4-pawn is not yet hanging because of Qd5+. }
11. O-O { The e4-pawn is not hanging yet because of  11...Nxe4  12.Qd5+  . }
11... Re8 12. Nc3 Kg8 13. Bg5
{ White is clearly better due to the space advantage and more active pieces. }
